ABOUT US

Welcome to Aura Nashik, a premier multi-cuisine restaurant and bar, where luxury, elegance, and flavor come together to offer a dining experience like no other. Situated in the heart of Nashik, we are committed to providing a sophisticated atmosphere, exquisite dishes, and unparalleled service. Whether you’re here for a family gathering, a special event, or a night out with friends, Aura Nashik is your destination for fine dining and memorable experiences.

READ MORE

A Culinary Journey at Aura

Indulge in a delightful fusion of flavors at Aura Nashik, where our multi-cuisine offerings bring together the best of global and local tastes. From authentic Indian spices to international delicacies, each dish is crafted to take your taste buds on an unforgettable journey. Experience exquisite flavors, innovative presentations, and a feast for all senses.

FAMILY RESTAURANT

Our Dining Experiences

At Aura, we offer a range of dining experiences to suit every mood and occasion:

  • Family Section: A warm, welcoming space for family gatherings, where comfort meets quality dining.

  • Moonlight Bar: An elegant space for those seeking to unwind with a refreshing drink under the stars, featuring an exclusive bar menu.

  • Banquet Hall: Perfect for hosting grand events, our banquet hall accommodates 80-100 guests for weddings, corporate events, birthdays, and more.

  • Club Night: Every Saturday and Sunday, our dance floor comes alive with vibrant music, creating the perfect atmosphere for fun-filled nights with friends.

Each space offers a unique vibe, ensuring an unforgettable dining experience at every visit.
